curam.util.exception

Class InformationalElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.exception.InformationalElement

  • public class InformationalElement
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used to describe an Informational Element. This can be used to build up an Exception or passed directly back to the client.
